    "intro_livre": {
      "type": "media-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Premier ouvrage — 2024</p>",
            "type_preset": "body",
            "font_size": "0.75rem",
            "letter_spacing": "0.2em",
            "case": "uppercase",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "titre": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Avant la Chute</h2>",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground-heading)"
          }
        },
        "sous_titre": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>L'Intelligence Préventive</em></p>",
            "type_preset": "h4",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "desc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>À travers 36 maximes de sagesse universelle, ce livre vous invite à développer la \"vigilance prospective\" : la capacité à anticiper, à lire l'invisible, à agir avant que le possible ne devienne irréversible.</p><p><em>Un livre pour ceux qui veulent cesser de subir — et commencer à prévoir.</em></p>",
            "type_preset": "body",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "cta": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Lire la présentation complète",
            "link": "/pages/le-livre",
            "style_class": "button-secondary"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["eyebrow", "titre", "sous_titre", "desc", "cta"],
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "media_position": "left",
        "media_width": "medium",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 80
      }
    },
    "intro_auteur": {
      "type": "media-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>L'Auteur</p>",
            "type_preset": "body",
            "font_size": "0.75rem",
            "letter_spacing": "0.2em",
            "case": "uppercase",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "nom": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Dr Mohamed Baidada</h2>",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground-heading)"
          }
        },
        "titre_auteur": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>Docteur en psychologie cognitive</em></p>",
            "type_preset": "h4",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "bio": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Ses travaux portent sur les mécanismes de la prise de décision en contexte d'incertitude, la cognition anticipative et les processus de résilience psychologique. Il a consacré sa thèse à l'étude de la métacognition comme outil de prévention des erreurs systémiques.</p>",
            "type_preset": "body",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "citation": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>« Mon ambition est simple : rendre la science du cerveau utile à la vie ordinaire. »</em></p>",
            "type_preset": "body",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
          }
        },
        "cta": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Découvrir l'auteur",
            "link": "/pages/auteur",
            "style_class": "button-secondary"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["eyebrow", "nom", "titre_auteur", "bio", "citation", "cta"],
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-3",
        "media_position": "right",
        "media_width": "medium",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 80,
        "padding-block-end": 80
